{"tid":532100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"辱台洋男引眾怒　抵制Twitch卻錯灌Twitter","createTime":"2018-01-17T12:55:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-18T10:19:40.000Z","uid":41818,"like":386,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"e62a77760e4ed884d4a139dd2fce63b5a134f784","tid":532100,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T12:55:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180117/640_01e654ab489b368387fbe2490ccdc997.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180117%2F640_01e654ab489b368387fbe2490ccdc997.jpg&h=7b1231cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左為《Twitch》，右為《Twitter》。引自Google Play<br />\n<br />\n躺著也種槍！在台生活的美籍直播主Cjayride，近日找來2女3男在摩鐵玩起泡泡浴，更稱「台女想吃洋腸」羞辱台灣女性。「館長」陳之漢火大到下戰帖，更宣布退出《Twitch》。台灣網友更發起起「一顆星」活動，揚言抵制《Twitch》，沒想到許多人卻都跑錯棚，到《Twitter》怒灌1顆星。<br />\n<br />\n辱台洋男事件爆發後，許多台灣網友認為直播平台《Twitch》的處理方式不公，除了在《臉書》粉專留言怒譙之外，甚至還有網友湧入《Twitch》的Google Play商店頁面留怒灌一顆星及負評並揚言抵制。不料，卻有不少網友跑錯棚到《Twitter》（推特）的APP下載頁面下嗆聲，並紛紛怒灌一顆星級複評，讓不少人看到都超傻眼。<br />\n<br />\n此事更被轉發至《PTT》引發熱議，許多網友趕緊跑到《Twitter》下載頁面灌滿5顆星幫「補血」，並留言「《Twitter》躺著也中槍」、「唸起來也差這麼多，到底在衝三小....」、「下一個抵制Twice了嗎？」、「我都不知道現在可以用Twitter看實況了」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180117/1280492/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180117%2F1280492%2F&d=WGx0PWGxoukb3bVjM6YW8EkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=dca76104\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180117%2F1280492%2F&h=cbb3cba5\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180117/1280492/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21e022c9494efce46bd26f62458dc7afbfd7c779","tid":532100,"uid":25424,"like":326,"dislike":0,"score":326,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T12:56:56.000Z","msg":"台狗英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img s